com.yworks.yfiles.graph.styles

Interface IShapeGeometry

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BevelNodeStyleRenderer, CollapsibleNodeStyleDecoratorRenderer, GeneralPathNodeStyleRenderer, ImageNodeStyleRenderer, MemoryImageNodeStyleRenderer, PanelNodeStyleRenderer, ShapeNodeStyleRenderer, ShinyPlateNodeStyleRenderer, TableNodeStyleRenderer, TemplateNodeStyleRenderer, VoidShapeGeometry

    public interface IShapeGeometry
    Interface that describes the geometry of a shape which has an interior and an exterior.

    • Method Summary

    • Method Detail

      • getIntersection

        PointD getIntersection(PointD inner,
                       PointD outer)
        Returns the intersection for the given line with this shape's geometry.
        Parameters:
        inner - The first point of the line that is inside the shape.
        outer - The second point of the line that is outside the shape.
        Returns:
        The coordinates of the intersection point, if an intersection was found.

      • getOutline

        GeneralPath getOutline()
        Returns the outline of the shape or null.
        Returns:
        The outline or null if no outline can be provided.

      • isInside

        boolean isInside(PointD location)
        Checks whether the given coordinate is deemed to lie within the shape's geometric bounds.
        Parameters:
        location - The point to test.
        Returns:
        True if the point lies within the shape.
